channel.title: ~Project Cz~
channel.description:
Hey all, I've been workin on a little project called Cz (nothing to do with Czar). Right now I'm working on the client, so I will show you what I have. It's based off of galkon's client, modified by butter and then me. Don't say "Amggg hez such a leech3r becuz he only changed picturez and st00fz!" Well, I've changed that, and some more. Remember, it's development for a reason :)
First, Some pictures of the client.
Here is the Main Page [IMG]http://i33.tinypic.com/16kxugo.png[/img] Here is the inv background,the log off button at the top works btw. [IMG]http://i487.photobucket.com/albums/rr236/musixblarring/cz4.jpg[/img]
and the stat icons
[IMG]http://i487.photobucket.com/albums/rr236/musixblarring/cz3.png[/img]
again, it's in development. Tell me any suggestions, comments, anything at all! thanks!
P.S. Removed the add models button (useless)
